### Get all notifications (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:8025/api/v1/notifications
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get all notifications with pagination
GET http://localhost:8025/api/v1/notifications?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get unread notification count
GET http://localhost:8025/api/v1/notifications/unread/count
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get notification by ID
GET http://localhost:8025/api/v1/notifications/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Create notification (as admin for any user)
POST http://localhost:8025/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <admin_token>

{
  "title": "Welcome!",
  "message": "Welcome to our platform. We're glad to have you here!",
  "type": "INFO",
  "userId": "target_user_id"
}

### Create notification (system generated for current user)
POST http://localhost:8025/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "title": "Profile Updated",
  "message": "Your profile has been successfully updated.",
  "type": "SUCCESS"
}

### Mark notification as read
PATCH http://localhost:8025/api/v1/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Mark all notifications as read
PATCH http://localhost:8025/api/v1/notifications/read/all
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Delete notification (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:8025/api/v1/notifications/1
Authorization: Bearer <token> 